{"tid":1555180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日去完美領之後發現咗個喺popo面隱身嘅裝扮","createTime":"2019-09-09T09:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T09:28:32.000Z","uid":107057,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"237175daaaa039d63a7213b09deba804f7fb3c0e","tid":1555180,"uid":107057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:13:18.000Z","msg":"話說我琴日聽咗連登講 full suit去見領事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走果陣我擺返件西裝外套入返迪仔嘅暴徒袋<br />\n加埋其他嘢 個袋好full 同時我又戴住黑色口罩<br />\n但我呢個裝扮可以自由穿梭於防暴<br />\n返到去自己果區嘅地鐵站又好多popo喺到捉人<br />\n但我喺佢哋面來回行幾次 佢哋都唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後大家可以準備裇衫 西褲去發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb26ae48d36577fe11e20550a2ca6cf977369a9","tid":1555180,"uid":221192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高爭鞋皮鞋點跑"},{"pid":"a04d9ad37732bbd25a0f5e6f00e8eb1bf099aeb5","tid":1555180,"uid":107057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edb26ae48d36577fe11e20550a2ca6cf977369a9","tid":1555180,"uid":221192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高爭鞋皮鞋點跑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:18:52.000Z","msg":"我著波鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a066ca14dc0ae3c8a369814d8622e508ba80678a","tid":1555180,"uid":221192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a04d9ad37732bbd25a0f5e6f00e8eb1bf099aeb5","tid":1555180,"uid":107057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edb26ae48d36577fe11e20550a2ca6cf977369a9","tid":1555180,"uid":221192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高爭鞋皮鞋點跑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:18:52.000